casebody.data:
Wednesday, October 23, 1991

MERIT DOCKET

90- 1588. Market/Media Research, Inc. v. Cuyahoga Cty. Court of Common Pleas.

In Prohibition. On motion to dismiss, motion to reconsider protective order, motion to deem matters admitted, suggestion of mootness, and motion to compel discovery. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
